sentences.sentence: She parcelled up the books to send.
sentences.translation: 她把要寄走的书包了起来。

sentences.sentence: The land was parcelled out into small lots.
sentences.translation: 这块地被分成了若干小块。

sentences.sentence: A child was not a "piece of property which can be parcelled up and moved around at will", he said.
sentences.translation: 孩子不是“随意打包与到处移动的一份财产”，他说。
